text: Kasur is a city in Pakistan. Kasur may also refer to: *Kasur District, a district of Punjab (Pakistan). *Kasur Tehsil, a tehsil of district Kasur. *Kasur station: **Kasur Junction railway station, a railway station situated in Kasur region. **Kasur Tehsil railway station, a railway station in Kasur tehsil. ==See also== *Kasuri (disambiguation) * *
